videos.description: Jimmy Butler shakes Brad Wanamaker and goes right by him for the and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler shakes Wanamaker for the and-1) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler shakes Wanamaker for the and-1

videos.description: Tyler Herro runs the pick-and-roll with Andre Iguodala to perfection for the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro drops dime to Iguodala for the dunk) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro drops dime to Iguodala for the dunk

videos.description: Jayson Tatum gets the steal and explodes to the rim for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum soars to the rim for the dunk) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum soars to the rim for the dunk

videos.description: Tyler Herro finds a cutting Bam Adebayo who double clutches on the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bam double clutches on the dunk) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam double clutches on the dunk

videos.description: Marcus Smart goes down the lane and gets the tough shot to fall with Goran Dragic all over him.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart gets tough shot to go through contact) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smart gets tough shot to go through contact

videos.description: Gordon Hayward finds himself wide-open underneath the basket, but he ends up missing the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (How did Hayward miss that?) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: How did Hayward miss that?

videos.description: Andre Iguodala steps up and knocks down a 3-pointer in transition, extending the Heat's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Iguodala drains his 4th 3 of the night) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iguodala drains his 4th 3 of the night

videos.description: Marcus Smart takes it away from Tyler Herro and crams home the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart strips Herro and flushes home the dunk) 2020/09/27 EHSEET

videos.headline: Smart strips Herro and flushes home the dunk

videos.description: Jaylen Brown gets upset about a foul not being called on Jimmy Butler for contact on his way to the rim for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brown injured after appearing to be clipped on dunk attempt) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown injured after appearing to be clipped on dunk attempt

videos.description: Bam Adebayo goes down the lane and emphatically slams home a dunk on Daniel Theis.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Adebayo crushes home monster dunk on Theis) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adebayo crushes home monster dunk on Theis

videos.description: Tyler Herro doesn't let Marcus Smart get in his way as he drives to the hoop for a clutch layup in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Herro blows by Smart for slick layup) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herro blows by Smart for slick layup

videos.description: Duncan Robinson cans the long 3-pointer putting the Heat up 15 with 2 minutes remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robinson ices game with deep 3-pointer) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson ices game with deep 3-pointer

videos.description: The Miami Heat dribble out the clock and congratulate the Celtics on a tough Eastern Conference Finals.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Celtics, Heat hug it out after tough-fought series) 2020/09/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Celtics, Heat hug it out after tough-fought series

videos.description: Bam Adebayo speaks to the large chip on the shoulder of his teammates and says their face-off with LeBron James and the Lakers will be a toss up.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Adebayo: 'We're not backing down from anybody') 2020/09/27

videos.headline: Adebayo: 'We're not backing down from anybody'
